				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/415/ramon-martinez-tells-what-happened-that-day">Ramon Martinez Tells  What Happened That Day</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/brian-doyle">Brian Doyle</a></li><li><a href="/issues/415">July 2010</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


